{"article_id":"WUXvDRVtX9qQ2Q5i","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Hillary Clinton said roughly three dozen times","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that she couldn ' t \" recall \" specific details or events","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"-- including training sessions","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"on handling classified information --","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"when FBI officials questioned her extensively about using a private email server while secretary of state ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"according to official documents","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"released Friday .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Clinton ' s responses were revealed in FBI documents about the roughly three-hour , July 2 interview","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"that concluded the agency ' s investigation","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"without recommending criminal charges ,","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"despite finding","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"that Clinton was \" extremely careless \"","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"in using the private server system for emails with classified government information .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"The newly-released documents did not reveal significant , new information about the federal government ' s probe into the issue ,","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"but they created more distractions for Clinton , the Democratic presidential nominee , and her campaign","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"as voters continue to question her trustworthiness .","depth":5},{"id":16,"text":"Clinton ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"who was secretary of state from 2009 to 2013 ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"said","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"she could not recall specific emails .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"But she also said","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"that she could not recall the details of briefings","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"on how to handle classified information .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"\" Clinton recalled","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"being briefed on Specific Access Program information","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"( for classified material . )","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"But could not recall any specific briefings","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"on how to handle information","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"associated with the SAPs , \"","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"the FBI said in the documents .","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"In another entry , the FBI addresses the issue","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"of Clinton using her BlackBerry","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"after being advised about the risks","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"of using her personal one .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"\" Clinton said","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"she requested a secured BlackBerry while at State","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"but could not recall","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"why they were unable to provide one , \"","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"according to the documents .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"In December 2012 , Clinton suffered a concussion from a purportedly fall","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"and weeks later developed a blood clot .","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"\" We are pleased","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"that the FBI has released the materials from Hillary Clinton 's interview ,","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"as we had requested , \"","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"campaign spokesman Brian Fallon said","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"after the documents were released .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"\" While her use of a single email account was clearly a mistake","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"and she has taken responsibility for it ,","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"these materials make clear","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"why the Justice Department believed","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"there was no basis","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"to move forward with this case . \"","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"Jason Miller , spokesman for Republican presidential nominee Donald Trump , said","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"the files \" reinforce Clinton ' s \" tremendously bad judgment and dishonesty . \"","depth":4},{"id":54,"text":"The several-dozen pages","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"released Friday","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"also show","depth":5},{"id":57,"text":"Clinton repeatedly claimed to have little training or understanding about the classification process","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"-- despite leading the department","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"that handled such information on a regular basis","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"and having a security clearance .","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"The document dump also revealed the gaps","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"that remain in the record .","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"Not only were numerous sections redacted ,","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"but the files showed","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"the FBI could not obtain 13 Clinton mobile devices","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"that may have been used","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"to send emails from her personal email address ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"in addition to two iPads .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"According to the files ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"Clinton claimed to have relied on the judgment of her aides and other officials","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"to handle classified material appropriately .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"She even told investigators","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"-- when asked what the \" C \" marking meant before a paragraph in an email","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"marked \" Confidential \" -","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"that \" she did not know","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"and could only speculate","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"it was referencing paragraphs","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"marked in alphabetical order . \"","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"The FBI document notes","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"that the email was in fact marked \" classified at the Confidential level. \"","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"when asked about different classification types like \" Top Secret , \"","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"Clinton went on to say","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"she \" did not pay","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"Clinton 's server was found to have more than 2,000 emails with classified material .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Most were retroactively classified ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"but FBI Director James Comey has disputed Clinton ' s insistence","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"that none of them were marked as such at the time .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"Clinton has repeatedly said","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"her use of private email was allowed .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"But in July she told FBI investigators","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"she `` did not explicitly request permission","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"to use a private server or email address , ''","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"the FBI wrote .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"They said","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"no one at the State Department raised concerns during her tenure ,","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"and that Clinton said","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"everyone","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"with whom she exchanged emails","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"knew","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"she was using a private email address .","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":203,"left":142,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":117,"right":141,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":114,"right":116,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":108,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":106,"right":107,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":106,"left":0,"right":105,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":105,"left":104,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":1,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":107,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration"